headline: Border Bank Chooses Jack Henry for Technology Modernization
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced today that Border Bank selected Jack Henry to upgrade its technology infrastructure. The decision was made to prepare the bank for growth and future needs, including improved customer experience and operational efficiencies.
